                    <h2>Daily Presence Practices</h2>                    <p>Each day is shaped by the way we live and what we practice. We have a choice to be in the Present moment or not.</p>                    <p>In addition to special teachings every month and Question and Answer sessions with Eckhart Tolle, you’ll also receive powerful Presence practices to incorporate into everyday life. </p>                    <p>By bringing more Presence into our work, our relationships and every area of our life, we are able to make everything a living practice. </p>                    <p>This is how we make lasting change and continually deepen into our experience of Presence.</p>
